Title: An Act Changing the Name of Every Emergency Hospital to District Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 176
An Act Changing the Name of Every Emergency Hospital to District Hospital
Section 1. Every emergency hospital shall hereafter be known as district hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
